# 🤖 AI Agent with n8n - My First Intelligent Automation Project

This is my **first AI agent**, created as a leap into the world of automation and intelligent systems. Built using [n8n](https://n8n.io/), this workflow demonstrates how to set up an AI-powered assistant that responds to messages and can perform tasks such as web search and calculations.

## 🧠 Features

- Uses **OpenAI Chat Model** for natural language understanding
- Maintains **conversation context** using Simple Memory
- Supports real-time responses to chat messages
- Integrates tools like:
  - 🔍 **SerpAPI** for search-based tasks
  - 🧮 **Calculator** for numeric computation

